'''bi-'''
# [[two]]
#{{chemistry}} containing twice as much of the specified group as normal
#: This is used in mixed metal & hydrogen salts, such as sodium bicarbonate. Its use in terms such as sodium bisulfide (instead of disulfide) is deprecated.

